<p>
Our Operations team is the hub at the center of many departmental spokes; we help hold the wheel together and move it forward. As an Operations Associate, you will be an integral player across all divisions of the company. Initially, your focus will be to help manage our inbound process, from tracking product shipping from vendors to troubleshooting exceptions in the receiving process at our warehouse. Other responsibilities might include assisting our eCommerce Operations team with product catalog updates, becoming officially White Belt certified, and supporting our Ninja team with customer service inquiries related to outbound orders and returns. You will also become a power user on a number of operations, inventory and fulfillment systems.</p>
<p>
Let&#39;s be honest, though; we&#39;re still a growing company that thinks like a start-up. If you need a rigid job description, this probably isn&#39;t the opportunity for you.</p>
<p>
This role will report into the Sr. Operations Associate and work with other lanes across the company from Accounting to Merchandising to Guideshops and Production. As part of the fastest-growing apparel brand ever launched on the internet, you will be able to get your hands dirty in a multitude of ever-evolving tasks and projects.</p>
